---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="DeepFunding - FAQ">
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h1>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">What is DeepFunding?</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              DeepFunding is a comprehensive funding platform designed to
              connect innovators with potential backers. We provide the tools
              and resources necessary to launch, fund, and manage your projects
              successfully.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
              How do I start a project?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              Getting started is easy! Simply create an account, click on "Start
              a Project" in your dashboard, and follow the step-by-step guide to
              set up your project page. You'll need to provide project details,
              funding goals, timeline, and rewards for backers.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
              What types of projects can be funded?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              We support a wide range of projects across various categories
              including technology, art, film, music, literature, science, and
              social initiatives. If you're unsure whether your project fits our
              platform, please contact our support team for guidance.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
              What fees does DeepFunding charge?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              DeepFunding charges a 5% platform fee on the total funds raised
              for successful projects. Additionally, there is a payment
              processing fee of approximately 3-5% depending on the payment
              method. Failed projects (those that don't reach their funding
              goal) are not charged any fees.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
              How is funding distributed?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              For successfully funded projects, funds are transferred to your
              designated account within 14 days after the campaign ends. We
              support various payout methods including bank transfers, PayPal,
              and other digital payment solutions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
              What happens if my project doesn't reach its funding goal?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              If your project doesn't reach its funding goal, no funds are
              collected from backers and no fees are charged. You're welcome to
              refine your project and launch it again with improvements based on
              the feedback received.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-card rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
              How can I promote my project?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground">
              We provide various promotional tools within our platform,
              including social media integration, embeddable widgets, and email
              campaign templates. Additionally, projects with unique concepts
              and strong presentations may be featured on our homepage and
              newsletter.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg mb-6">Still have questions? We're here to help!</p>
          <a
            href="#"
            class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity inline-block"
          >
            Contact Support
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

